title: Second Date Update: Bad Boy or Just Boy
itunes:title: Second Date Update: Bad Boy or Just Boy
description: If you're on a date and the guy says he has a surprise for you in his coat pocket...Do you immediately think weapon... or two pouches of warm liquid? Well, one of those was the right answer today...and it could be the reason he's not getting a call back...
